# Secrets — do not commit
.cursor/mcp.json

# Demo output (may contain record ids)
scripts/blob-log.session5.json

# Copy delegate key into `.cursor/mcp.json` locally only:

```
MEMWAL_PRIVATE_KEY=<from ~/.memwal/credentials.json after memwal login --prod>
```

Never commit real keys. The template uses `REPLACE_WITH_DELEGATE_KEY_FROM_memwal_login`.
